GraphDTA GitHub
DeepDTA GitHub

ğŸ§  Applications
The KIBA dataset is widely used in:
Binding affinity regression models
Deep learning (CNN, GNN, Transformer, FAVAR-GAT)
Drug repurposing and virtual screening
